					<description><![CDATA[Amazon Business is available again for university purchases made with a P-Card.]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Amazon Business is available again for university purchases made with a P-Card.</p>
<p>Former Amazon Business Account members will receive an email once their account has been activated. P-Cardholders who have not previously held an Amazon Business Account membership can <a href="http://business.amazon.com">request an Amazon Business account</a>.</p>
<p>The new Amazon Business account offers many business-specific benefits, including:</p>
<ul>
<li>Prime-only purchases, ensuring best value and compliance with Illinois law.</li>
<li>Automatic tax-exempt purchasing on items sold by Amazon.com LLC and participating third-party sellers.</li>
<li>Access to millions of additional products, available only to business customers.</li>
<li>Business-specific pricing, including quantity discounts on eligible items.</li>
<li>Access to a specialized Amazon Business customer service team.</li>
<li>University P-Card purchases only, for a seamless reconciliation.</li>
<li>Prohibition on personal purchases, eliminating denials in reimbursement.</li>
</ul>
<p>Questions can be directed to <a title="mailto:UICPurchasing@uillinois.edu" href="mailto:UICPurchasing@uillinois.edu">UICPurchasing@uillinois.edu</a>.</p>
