					<description><![CDATA[Employees may be eligible to defer a portion of their vacation leave payout to their University 403(b) and/or 457 Plan retirement accounts]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>UIC employees may be eligible to defer a portion of their vacation leave payout to their university 403(b) and/or 457 Plan retirement accounts when retiring or separating from the university.</p>
<p>To defer your payout, contact University Payroll &amp; Benefits at least 60 days prior to your last day of employment. Create a <a href="https://www.obfs.uillinois.edu/payroll/customer-service/">UPB Service Ticket</a> or call 312-996-7200.</p>
<p>View <a href="https://www.hr.uillinois.edu/benefits/retirement/separationprep#termpayout">Leave Payout</a> for more information.</p>
