<p>UIC Human Resources is announcing the 2022 UIC Award Season and a call for nominations for the Award of Merit.</p>
<p>The Award of Merit is designed to recognize exceptional employees from all corners of the university serving in all levels of Civil Service and Academic Professional positions. We encourage you to consider nominating an outstanding Civil Service or Academic Professional employee for this award. Employees based at the regional campuses and Chicago-based units of the University of Illinois System are also eligible to nominate and receive this award.</p>
